video_title: Get your hands on my new  book if you want my help with many other strategies to hit your goals.
transcript:
if you want to be successful there's one
really important question to ask
yourself many times per day the question
is this is what I'm doing right now
getting me closer to or further from my
goals if the answer is closer to then
just keep going but if the answer is
further from stop what you're doing
immediately and take a different action
that will get you closer to where you
want to be in life
